436
00:33:09,572 --> 00:33:13,201
A trecut ceva vreme. Am şolduri cam mari.

437
00:33:13,284 --> 00:33:14,911
Da.

438
00:33:14,995 --> 00:33:16,997
Pune-o, Nathe.

439
00:33:17,080 --> 00:33:19,290
Fă ce poţi, amice.

440
00:34:01,624 --> 00:34:03,918
